I over heard a conversation with a hotel staff member and a guest, and apparently someone let their kids sleep in the car in the parking lot all night!	Our favorite part of the stay is enjoying the massage and spa treatments at the Baths which are located across the parking lot from the hotel.	I can leave the car in the parking lot until we leave town.	There is adequate parking and everything in town is within walking distance.	Right next door is the Oasis mud bath and massage spa, only a few feet from the hotel.